<div class="mt-8">
    <div class="font-headline text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-black dark:text-white">
        Diesen Artikel teilen
    </div>
    <p>
        Wenn dir der Artikel gefallen hat oder du denkst, dass die Informationen auch für andere hilfreich sein könnten, teile
        ihn gerne. Damit hilfst du nicht nur anderen, sondern unterstützt auch meine Arbeit und den Blog.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <button type="button" data-web-share data-title="{{title}}"
            data-text="{{#if custom_excerpt}}{{custom_excerpt}}{{else}}{{excerpt}}{{/if}}" data-url="{{url absolute="
            true"}}"
            class="hidden items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 cursor-pointer text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition dark:bg-white dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-neutral-200">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                    d="M8.684 13.342C8.886 12.938 9 12.482 9 12c0-.482-.114-.938-.316-1.342m0 2.684a3 3 0 110-2.684m0 2.684l6.632 3.316m-6.632-6l6.632-3.316m0 0a3 3 0 105.367-2.684 3 3 0 00-5.367 2.684zm0 9.316a3 3 0 105.368 2.684 3 3 0 00-5.368-2.684z" />
            </svg>
            {{#unless hideLabel}}Teilen{{/unless}}
        </button>

        <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text={{encode title}}&url={{url absolute=" true"}}" target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 cursor-pointer text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition dark:bg-white dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-neutral-200">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path
                    d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z" />
            </svg>
            {{#unless hideLabel}}Twitter/X{{/unless}}
        </a>
        <a href="https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url={{url absolute=" true"}}&media={{#if feature_image}}{{img_url
            feature_image size="l" }}{{else}}{{@site.cover_image}}{{/if}}&description={{encode title}}" target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 cursor-pointer text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition dark:bg-white dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-neutral-200">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path
                    d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.372 0 12c0 5.084 3.163 9.426 7.627 11.174-.105-.949-.2-2.405.042-3.441.218-.937 1.407-5.965 1.407-5.965s-.359-.719-.359-1.782c0-1.668.967-2.914 2.171-2.914 1.023 0 1.518.769 1.518 1.69 0 1.029-.655 2.568-.994 3.995-.283 1.194.599 2.169 1.777 2.169 2.133 0 3.772-2.249 3.772-5.495 0-2.873-2.064-4.882-5.012-4.882-3.414 0-5.418 2.561-5.418 5.207 0 1.031.397 2.138.893 2.738.098.119.112.224.083.345l-.333 1.36c-.053.22-.174.267-.402.161-1.499-.698-2.436-2.889-2.436-4.649 0-3.785 2.75-7.262 7.929-7.262 4.163 0 7.398 2.967 7.398 6.931 0 4.136-2.607 7.464-6.227 7.464-1.216 0-2.359-.631-2.75-1.378l-.748 2.853c-.271 1.043-1.002 2.35-1.492 3.146C9.57 23.812 10.763 24 12 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12 0-6.628-5.373-12-12-12z" />
            </svg>
            {{#unless hideLabel}}Pinterest{{/unless}}
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url={{url absolute=" true"}}" target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 cursor-pointer text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition dark:bg-white dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-neutral-200">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path
                    d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z" />
            </svg>
            {{#unless hideLabel}}LinkedIn{{/unless}}
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:?subject={{encode title}}&body={{url absolute=" true"}}"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 cursor-pointer text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition dark:bg-white dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-neutral-200">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                    d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            E-Mail
        </a>
        <button type="button" data-share-copy data-url="{{url absolute=" true"}}"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-neutral-100 cursor-pointer text-black font-semibold text-xs rounded-full hover:bg-neutral-200 transition dark:bg-white dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-neutral-200">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                    d="M8 16H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v2m-6 12h8a2 2 0 002-2v-8a2 2 0 00-2-2h-8a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <span data-share-copy-text>Link kopieren</span>
        </button>
    </div>
</div>